text_block_list.name: Symboli Kris S
text_block_list.text: Sometimes, I can feel…… your gaze.

text_block_list.name: Symboli Kris S
text_block_list.text:
Is there something…… 
you want to say to me?

text_block_list.name: Zenno Rob Roy
text_block_list.text:
S-S-S-Sorry!! Umm……I can't help but 
be curious about your demeanor and how 
cool you act……

text_block_list.name: Symboli Kris S
text_block_list.text:
Do you find it unpleasant? If there is 
something I should correct, I will.

text_block_list.name: Zenno Rob Roy
text_block_list.text:
No, not at all……! You're like a 
cool, hard-boiled protagonist from 
a novel… I think it's wonderful!

text_block_list.name: Symboli Kris S
text_block_list.text: Is that so. I don't…… really understand.

text_block_list.name: Zenno Rob Roy
text_block_list.text:
Ah!! I-It's moments just like that! That
sorrowful air about you is just like the
protagonist from "Agent Horsegirl"……!

text_block_list.name: Zenno Rob Roy
text_block_list.text:
Ahh, that expression too……! You look 
exactly like when she gets stuck during 
a mission and is contemplating what to 
do next……!

text_block_list.name: Zenno Rob Roy
text_block_list.text:
…… U-Umm…… If it's alright with you……
could you please say a line an agent
would say after completing a mission……?
